    "Process P 1 is designed to get the raw water into the system.",
    "P 2 is focused on chemical dosing and P 3 with ultra-filtration.",
    "P 4 includes UV-dechlorination and P 5 carries out reverse osmosis (RO).",
    "P 6 uses a backwash tank for cleaning and stores treated water in another tank (that is recycled).",
    "The device names consist of two parts where the first 3 characters are shortened for devices type and the last 3 numbers refer to the process stage and number of devices."
